{
  "texts": [
    "It is important to recognize that a comprehensive grasp of fundamental mathematical concepts cannot be achieved solely through the depiction of mathematical objects and figures; rather, creative and dynamic practices are needed (Velichová, 2011).",
    "GeoGebra facilitates such practices by enabling users to navigate multiple mathematical representations (Velichová, 2011).",
    "The software's structure fosters an interactive and engaging learning environment in which students can enthusiastically explore and visualize mathematical concepts, thereby enhancing their comprehension and problem-solving abilities.",
    "However, it must be acknowledged that despite its effectiveness in education, using GeoGebra alone does not guarantee successful teaching outcomes.",
    "Teachers with the necessary knowledge and skills play a pivotal role in employing GeoGebra effectively and designing relevant activities as they are a key part of the instructional process (Laborde, 2007)."
  ]
}